
astroTools README


The astroTools package provides assorted tools that can be used for astronomy and 
astrophysics.  For compilation you can use CMake (available at http://www.cmake.org/).  
To download the astroTools package, read the code documentation, or to contact the 
developers, see: 

http://astrotools.sourceforge.net/



INSTALLATION:

For installation instructions, see INSTALL.



